---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | PDF Editor">
  <div class="py-24 bg-white flex-1">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl prose prose-slate">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 text-slate-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. File Security and Processing</h2>
        <p>Your privacy is our primary concern. When you upload a PDF file to our servers for processing:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>All transfers are secured using 256-bit SSL encryption.</li>
          <li>Files are processed completely automatically by our systems. No human ever sees or accesses your documents.</li>
          <li>We do not analyze, mine, or extract any data from your files.</li>
          <li><strong>All uploaded files and processed output files are permanently deleted from our servers within 2 hours of processing.</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Data Collection</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal information necessary to provide our service:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Standard web analytics (IP address, browser type, pages visited) to improve our service.</li>
          <li>Account information (email, name) only if you choose to register for a paid plan.</li>
          <li>Payment information is processed securely by our payment provider (Stripe) and never touches our servers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@onlinepdfeditorfree.com.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>